column16: Cesar Izturis flies out to left fielder Chris Coghlan.
Craig Tatum doubles (2) on a line drive to center fielder Cody Ross.    Adam Jones scores.
Jake Fox flies out to center fielder Cody Ross.
Adam Jones singles on a sharp ground ball to center fielder Cody Ross.
Corey Patterson flies out to left fielder Chris Coghlan.
Dioner Navarro grounds out to first baseman Gaby Sanchez.
Jason Bartlett singles on a soft ground ball to center fielder Cody Ross, deflected by shortstop Brian Barden.    Ben Zobrist scores.   Upton scores.    Reid Brignac to 3rd.
Carl Crawford flies out to left fielder Chris Coghlan in foul territory.
B.  J.   Upton singles on a line drive to center fielder Cody Ross.    Hank Blalock scores.
Hank Blalock doubles (3) on a fly ball to right fielder Mike Stanton.
